*--------------*
|    Files     |
*--------------*

* bower.json
* package.json

contain dependencies when running a test web server with nodejs & npm and should not be put on the productive web server.
See https://docs.angularjs.org/tutorial for more details.

*.htaccess

contains project specific configuration for the Apache web server (such as URL rewrite rules).


*--------------------------------*
|    Deployment on Production    |
*--------------------------------*

Compress mindliner.css (e.g. via http://csscompressor.com/) and save as
* mindliner.min.css

Do not forget to change to mindliner.min.css on production.
Note: There is no straightforward way to minify a AngularJS file afaik.

